## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

#### Uncommitted Changes
```bash
# Check status
git status

# Stash changes
git stash

# Apply stashed changes
git stash pop

# List stashes
git stash list
```

#### Merge Conflicts
```bash
# Abort merge
git merge --abort

# Abort rebase
git rebase --abort

# Reset to previous state
git reset --hard HEAD~1
```

#### Tag Issues
```bash
# Delete local tag
git tag -d v1.1.0

# Delete remote tag
git push origin :refs/tags/v1.1.0

# Recreate tag
git tag -a v1.1.0 -m "Release version 1.1.0"
```

#### Branch Issues
```bash
# Delete local branch
git branch -d feature-branch

# Delete remote branch
git push origin --delete feature-branch

# Force delete local branch
git branch -D feature-branch
```

